text: The 2019 Temple Owls men's soccer team represented Temple University during the 2019 NCAA Division I men's soccer season and the 2019 American Athletic Conference men's soccer season. The regular season began on August 29 and concluded on November 5. It was the program's 94th season fielding a men's varsity soccer team, and their 7th season in the AAC.
